<H3> <TI>   Juppe: Helicopter Crews To Ignore Serb Controls </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Juppe: Helicopter Crews To Ignore Serb Controls </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2604085094 Paris Radio France International in French 0800 
GMT 26 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2604085094 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris Radio France International </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] France says the controls imposed by the Serbs on the 
evacuation by helicopter of wounded people from Gorazde are 
unacceptable. Paris ordered the crews of French helicopters 
involved in these missions to refuse to submit to these 
controls. This was stressed by the French Foreign Ministry 
yesterday evening. These Serb controls are reported to have 
quadrupled travelling times for the evacuations. 

</TEXT>

