  [Text] Foreign Minister Klaus Kinkel has received his 
Russian counterpart, Kozyrev, for political talks in Bonn today. 
The meeting will focus on preparations for President Yeltsin's 
visit to Germany, scheduled for mid-May. Kinkel and Kozyrev 
