<H3> <TI>   Italy To Host NATO's `Dynamic Impact' Maneuvers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Italy To Host NATO's `Dynamic Impact' Maneuvers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2604131894 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1102 GMT 26 
