<H3> <TI>   Delcroix on Military Cooperation With Netherlands </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Delcroix on Military Cooperation With Netherlands </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2604131694 Brussels BELGA Database in French 1752 GMT 25 
Apr 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR2604131694 </F>
<F P=104>  Brussels BELGA Database </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


<TEXT>
