------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|--foreign orders                      |-\11.6                                | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Basic materials and producer goods    |+\12.3                                | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Investment goods                      |+\30.6                                | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Consumer goods                        |+\28.2                                | 
