<H3> <TI>   Slovene Defense Delegation Attends </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Slovene Defense Delegation Attends </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2804175894 Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network in Slovene 
1330 GMT 28 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU2804175894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network </F>
<F P=105>  Slovene </F>


<TEXT>
