<H3> <TI>   Italy Warned on Borders </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Italy Warned on Borders </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2804112894 Vienna KURIER in German 28 Apr 94 p 5 </F>
