  [Text] Veronika Seyr, the Belgrade correspondent of 
Austrian Radio and Television, ORF, was detained by the Serbs. 
After filming television shots in Gorazde, Seyr had her film 
and equipment taken away by the Serbs and was released only 
after several hours of interrogation. 

